---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PHCDevworks"
  description="Design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure. Open source. Built for developers."
>
  <section style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem;">
    <article style="margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h1
        class="brand"
        style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 7rem); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 2rem;"
      >
        PHCDEVWORKS
      </h1>
      <p
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 900px;"
      >
        We build design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p
        class="muted-text"
        style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 700px;"
      >
        Everything is open source. Everything is on GitHub.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="divider" style="padding-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h2
        style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Projects
      </h2>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 4rem;">
        <div style="border-left: 3px solid #ff5757; padding-left: 2rem;">
          <h3
            style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-tokens"
              class="link"
              style="border-bottom-width: 3px;"
            >
              Spectre Tokens
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p
            class="muted-text"
            style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px;"
          >
            Core design primitives for the Spectre suite. Colors, spacing,
            typography, radii, shadows. Outputs to CSS variables, JS/TS objects,
            and theme presets for WordPress, Astro, 11ty.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left: 3px solid #ff5757; padding-left: 2rem;">
          <h3
            style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui"
              class="link"
              style="border-bottom-width: 3px;"
            >
              Spectre UI
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p
            class="muted-text"
            style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px;"
          >
            Cross-platform UI built on Spectre Tokens. Tailwind-powered design
            system delivering consistent CSS utilities, component classes, and
            design recipes for WordPress, Astro, 11ty.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left: 3px solid #ff5757; padding-left: 2rem;">
          <h3
            style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui-astro"
              class="link"
              style="border-bottom-width: 3px;"
            >
              Spectre UI Astro
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p
            class="muted-text"
            style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px;"
          >
            First-class Astro layer for Spectre UI. Typed, SSR-friendly
            components (Button, Card, Input) that wrap Spectre UI classes and
            tokens. Native Astro, zero bloat.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left: 3px solid #ff5757; padding-left: 2rem;">
          <h3
            style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-icons"
              class="link"
              style="border-bottom-width: 3px;"
            >
              Spectre Icons
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p
            class="muted-text"
            style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px;"
          >
            Modern SVG icon sets for WordPress builders. Lucide, Font Awesome,
            and more. Unified manager, performance-first. Replaces dozens of
            separate icon plugins.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="divider" style="padding-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h2
        style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Philosophy
      </h2>
      <div style="display: grid; gap: 2.5rem; max-width: 900px;">
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;"
        >
          Design tokens once.<br />
          <span class="accent-text">Use everywhere.</span>
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;"
        >
          Tokens feed CSS.<br />
          <span class="accent-text">CSS feeds components.</span>
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;"
        >
          Open source.<br />
          <span class="accent-text">No vendor lock.</span>
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;"
        >
          Build what you need.<br />
          <span class="accent-text">Modify what you want.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="divider" style="padding-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 800;">
        Links
      </h2>
      <div>
        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <a href="https://github.com/phcdevworks" class="link">
            github.com/phcdevworks
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
          All repos. All docs. All roadmaps.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <footer class="divider" style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 0.875rem;">Â© 2025 PHCDevworks</p>
    </footer>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
